{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make short selling shares illegal in the UK",
        "additional_details": "How on earth can some other company loan out something you own without your consent? I believe that it amounts to legal theft authorised by the government, I think it is open to abuse, and needs to be banned and stopped.",
        "background": "I believe short selling of stocks in the UK causes instability in companies share prices.",
